  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Compare and contrast the six known quarks</item>
<item>Use quark composition of hadrons to determine the total charge of these particles</item>
<item>Explain the primary evidence for the existence of quarks</item></list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
